fields.Title: Chicken Biryani
fields.Description: Chicken Biryani is a traditional and aromatic South Asian dish made with basmati rice, tender chicken, and a blend of fragrant spices. It is a perfect balance of flavors, featuring layers of marinated chicken, spiced rice, caramelized onions, and saffron-infused milk.
fields.Ingrediants: chicken, masale, salt, Rise
fields.Instructions:
In a large bowl, mix yogurt, ginger-garlic paste, red chili powder, turmeric powder, garam masala, salt, lemon juice, and oil.
Add chicken pieces and coat them well in the marinade.

fields.Title: Anda Biryani
fields.Description: Anda Biryani is a flavorful and aromatic rice dish made with boiled eggs, basmati rice, and a blend of rich Indian spices. This easy-to-make biryani is perfect for a quick yet delicious meal, offering a perfect balance of spice and aroma. Serve it with raita or salad for a complete experience!.
fields.Ingrediants: Ande, masale, salt, Rise , Water
fields.Instructions:
Boil the Eggs – Boil the eggs, peel them, and make small slits on their surface to absorb the flavors.

Prepare the Rice – Wash and soak basmati rice for 30 minutes. Cook until 80% done, then drain and set aside.

fields.Title: Chicken Fry
fields.Description: Chicken Fry is a crispy, flavorful, and spicy dish made by marinating chicken with aromatic spices and frying it to golden perfection. It is a popular side dish enjoyed with rice, roti, or as an appetizer. With a perfect balance of crunch and juiciness.
fields.Ingrediants: chicken, masale, salt,, Water, Oil
fields.Instructions:
Marinate the Chicken – In a bowl, mix chicken pieces with yogurt, turmeric, red chili powder, garam masala, ginger-garlic paste, salt, and lemon juice. Let it marinate for at least 30 minutes (or overnight for better flavor).

Heat Oil – In a pan, heat oil or ghee on medium flame.

fields.Title: Fish Fry
fields.Description: Fish Fry is a crispy and flavorful dish made by marinating fish fillets with spices, herbs, and lemon juice, then coating them with flour or breadcrumbs before deep or shallow frying. This dish is known for its crunchy exterior and tender, juicy inside. It is often served with chutney, salad.
fields.Ingrediants: Fish, masale, salt,, Water, Oil
fields.Instructions:
Clean the Fish – Wash the fish fillets thoroughly under running water and pat them dry with a paper towel.

Prepare the Marinade – In a bowl, mix turmeric, red chili powder, salt, ginger-garlic paste, lemon juice, and any preferred spices.

fields.Title: Chilli
fields.Description: Chilli is a rich, flavorful dish made with beans, tomatoes, spices, and either meat or a vegetarian alternative. Slow-cooked to perfection, it offers a perfect balance of heat and taste. This versatile recipe is easy to make, customizable, and packed with nutrients. Serve it with rice, bread.
fields.Ingrediants: Heat Oil, Sauté Aromatics, Cook Meat, Add Tomatoes & Beans,
fields.Instructions:
Gather all ingredients, including chopped onions, minced garlic, ground meat (or vegetarian alternative), diced tomatoes, kidney beans, tomato paste, and spices.

Heat oil in a large pot over medium heat. Add chopped onions and garlic, cooking until they become soft and fragrant.

fields.Title: Fried Noodles
fields.Description: Fried noodles are a delicious and versatile dish made by stir-frying noodles with a mix of vegetables, protein (chicken, shrimp, or tofu), and savory sauces. This quick and easy recipe delivers a perfect balance of crispy texture, bold flavors, and vibrant colors. Commonly found in Asian cuisine.
fields.Ingrediants: 200g noodles (boiled), 2 tbsp oil, 1 onion (sliced), 2 garlic cloves (minced)
fields.Instructions: Instructions: Boil noodles, sauté onions and garlic in oil, cook protein (if using), add vegetables, mix in noodles with sauces and seasoning, stir-fry for 2 minutes, garnish, and serve hot!

fields.Title: Mutton Biryani
fields.Description: Mutton Biryani is a rich and aromatic rice dish made with tender mutton, fragrant basmati rice, and a blend of exotic spices. Slow-cooked to perfection, this dish is layered with caramelized onions, yogurt, saffron, and fresh herbs, creating a mouthwatering explosion of flavors.
fields.Ingrediants: Mutton, basmati rice, onions, tomatoes, yogurt, ginger-garlic paste, green chilies, biryani masala.
fields.Instructions: Marinate mutton with yogurt and spices, cook until tender, parboil rice with whole spices, layer mutton and rice with fried onions, saffron, and mint, seal and dum cook for 20-30 minutes, then serve hot with raita!

fields.Title: Greek Salad
fields.Description: Greek Salad is a refreshing Mediterranean dish made with crisp cucumbers, juicy tomatoes, crunchy bell peppers, red onions, Kalamata olives, and creamy feta cheese. Tossed with olive oil, oregano, and a splash of lemon juice, this salad offers a perfect balance of tangy, salty, and fresh flavors.
fields.Ingrediants: Cucumbers, tomatoes, bell peppers, red onions, Kalamata olives, feta cheese, olive oil, lemon juice, oregano, salt, and black pepper.
fields.Instructions: Chop all vegetables, mix with olives and feta cheese, drizzle with olive oil and lemon juice, season with oregano, salt, and pepper, toss well, and serve fresh!

fields.Title: Green Salad
fields.Description: A light, fresh, and healthy salad made with leafy greens, crunchy vegetables, and a simple dressing for a nutritious meal.
fields.Ingrediants: Lettuce, spinach, cucumbers, tomatoes, carrots, bell peppers, onions, olive oil, lemon juice, salt, black pepper, and optional nuts or seeds.
fields.Instructions: Chop all vegetables, mix in a bowl, drizzle with olive oil and lemon juice, season with salt and pepper, toss well, and serve fresh!

fields.Title: Italian Salad
fields.Description: A vibrant and flavorful salad made with fresh greens, juicy tomatoes, olives, and Italian dressing, perfect as a side or light meal.
fields.Ingrediants: Romaine lettuce, cherry tomatoes, red onions, black olives, bell peppers, parmesan cheese, croutons, olive oil, red wine vinegar, Italian seasoning, salt, and black pepper.
fields.Instructions: Chop vegetables, mix in a bowl with olives and croutons, drizzle with olive oil and vinegar, season with Italian herbs, toss well, and serve fresh!

fields.Title: Manchurian
fields.Description: A popular Indo-Chinese dish made with crispy vegetable or chicken balls tossed in a spicy, tangy, and flavorful Manchurian sauce.
fields.Ingrediants: Cabbage, carrots, capsicum, garlic, ginger, soy sauce, chili sauce, vinegar, cornstarch, all-purpose flour, spring onions, black pepper, salt, and oil.
fields.Instructions: Mix grated veggies with flour and cornstarch, shape into balls, deep-fry until golden, stir-fry with garlic, ginger, and sauces, coat well, and serve hot!

fields.Title: Manchurian Noodles
fields.Description: A delicious Indo-Chinese fusion dish combining crispy Manchurian balls with stir-fried noodles in a spicy, tangy sauce.
fields.Ingrediants: Noodles, cabbage, carrots, capsicum, garlic, ginger, soy sauce, chili sauce, vinegar, cornstarch, all-purpose flour, spring onions, black pepper, salt, and oil.
fields.Instructions: Boil noodles, prepare and fry Manchurian balls, stir-fry vegetables with garlic and ginger, add sauces and seasonings, toss in noodles and Manchurian balls, mix well, and serve hot!

fields.Title: Nikoise Salad
fields.Description: A classic French salad made with fresh vegetables, tuna, eggs, and olives, dressed in a light vinaigrette for a refreshing and hearty meal.
fields.Ingrediants: Lettuce, cherry tomatoes, boiled potatoes, green beans, tuna, hard-boiled eggs, black olives, red onions, olive oil, Dijon mustard, lemon juice, salt, and black pepper.
fields.Instructions: Boil potatoes, green beans, and eggs, arrange with tuna and vegetables on a plate, drizzle with olive oil and mustard dressing, toss gently, and serve fresh!

fields.Title: Pasta
fields.Description: A classic Italian dish made with boiled pasta, rich sauces, and flavorful ingredients, perfect for a satisfying meal.
fields.Ingrediants: Pasta (penne, spaghetti, or any type), olive oil, garlic, onions, tomatoes, tomato sauce, chili flakes, black pepper, salt, basil, parmesan cheese, and optional vegetables or protein (chicken, shrimp, or tofu).
fields.Instructions: Boil pasta until al dente, sauté garlic and onions in olive oil, add tomato sauce and seasonings, mix in pasta, toss well, garnish with parmesan and basil, and serve hot!

fields.Title: Pav Bhaji
fields.Description: A popular Indian street food dish made with a spicy, mashed vegetable curry served with butter-toasted pav (bread rolls).
fields.Ingrediants: Potatoes, tomatoes, onions, capsicum, peas, garlic, ginger, butter, pav bhaji masala, red chili powder, salt, lemon juice, coriander leaves, and pav (bread rolls).
fields.Instructions: Boil and mash vegetables, sauté onions, garlic, and spices in butter, mix in mashed veggies, cook until thick, toast pav with butter, garnish bhaji with coriander and lemon, and serve hot!

fields.Title: Shev Bhaji
fields.Description: A spicy and flavorful Maharashtrian curry made with crispy shev (gram flour noodles) cooked in a rich onion-tomato gravy, served with bhakri or roti.
fields.Ingrediants: Shev, onions, tomatoes, garlic, ginger, green chilies, red chili powder, turmeric, garam masala, coriander powder, cumin seeds, salt, oil, water, and fresh coriander for garnish.
fields.Instructions: Sauté onions, garlic, and spices in oil, add tomatoes and cook until soft, pour water to make gravy, add shev just before serving, garnish with coriander, and enjoy with roti or bhakri!

fields.Title: vegetable Pulao
fields.Description: A fragrant and mildly spiced rice dish cooked with mixed vegetables and aromatic spices, perfect for a wholesome meal.
fields.Ingrediants: Basmati rice, onions, tomatoes, carrots, peas, beans, potatoes, green chilies, garlic, ginger, bay leaves, cloves, cinnamon, cardamom, cumin seeds, turmeric, garam masala, salt, oil, and coriander for garnish.
fields.Instructions: Sauté spices, onions, and ginger-garlic in oil, add vegetables and rice, mix well, pour water, cook until rice is fluffy, garnish with coriander, and serve hot!

fields.Title: vegetable stir fry
fields.Description: A quick and healthy dish made by stir-frying fresh vegetables in a flavorful sauce, perfect as a side or main dish.
fields.Ingrediants: Mixed vegetables (broccoli, bell peppers, carrots, beans, mushrooms), garlic, ginger, soy sauce, chili sauce, vinegar, black pepper, salt, and sesame oil.
fields.Instructions: Heat oil, sauté garlic and ginger, add vegetables, stir-fry on high heat, mix in sauces and seasoning, toss well, and serve hot!

fields.Title: Chana Masala
fields.Description: A spicy and flavorful North Indian curry made with chickpeas cooked in a rich tomato-onion gravy, perfect with rice or roti.
fields.Ingrediants: Chickpeas (chana), onions, tomatoes, garlic, ginger, green chilies, cumin seeds, coriander powder, turmeric, red chili powder, garam masala, chana masala, salt, oil, and fresh coriander for garnish.
fields.Instructions: Sauté onions, garlic, and spices in oil, add tomatoes and cook until soft, mix in boiled chickpeas, simmer until thick, garnish with coriander, and serve hot!

fields.Title: Muttor Paneer
fields.Description: A rich and creamy North Indian curry made with soft paneer (cottage cheese) and green peas cooked in a flavorful tomato-onion gravy.
fields.Ingrediants: Paneer, green peas, onions, tomatoes, ginger, garlic, green chilies, cumin seeds, turmeric, red chili powder, garam masala, coriander powder, salt, cream (optional), oil, and fresh coriander for garnish.
fields.Instructions: Sauté onions, garlic, and spices in oil, add tomatoes and cook until soft, mix in peas and paneer, simmer until thick, garnish with coriander, and serve hot with roti or rice!

fields.Title: Sandwich
fields.Description: A delicious, crispy, and cheesy snack perfect for any time of the day.
fields.Ingrediants: Bread, cheese, butter.
fields.Instructions: Spread butter on bread, place cheese between slices, grill until golden and crispy. Enjoy!
